Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是關於電腦的案件
